<span id="freeTextContainer334594221111224550">Loved it!!! I LOVE time-travel/historical fiction/alternate reality stories. I am also in love with books that can broaden my horizons, tell a compelling story, and have great writing. This definitely fit the bill. It is well written, had a great plot, the characters were interesting, and it was thought provoking.<br/><br/>My love of this genre started for me with &quot;the Magic Tunnel&quot; where children travel back to 1664, when New York was New Amsterdam. I also loved &quot;The Devil&apos;s Arithmetic&quot; where 12 year old</span>
